{"tid":193762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丟手機兒跟著跳樓亡　父抱屍痛哭","createTime":"2017-04-09T13:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T16:28:55.000Z","uid":22736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b18732caf0088ab30457ff766811915315b5a2d9","tid":193762,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/international/275068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Fbreakingnews%2Finternational%2F275068&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=083c54fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/international/275068</a><br />\n中國遼寧省一名就讀國中的少年沉迷玩手機，父親奪走他手機後扔下樓，沒想到少年竟跟著手機一起墜樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n近日微博瘋傳這段影片，一名年輕男子躺在地上，中年男子抱著屍體哀號、痛哭失聲！拍攝影片的女子感嘆：「好傻啊！這孩子！」<br />\n<br />\n根據中國媒體報導，這名爸爸疑似不滿兒子顧著玩手機，一氣之下將手機搶走，丟出窗外，沒想到少年竟跟著一躍而下，父親抱著躺在地上的兒子遺體，痛哭失聲！（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b63Z38S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb63Z38S.jpg&h=abb3032e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43315dfdc3b1d4f56f32445f598b382eee28205c","tid":193762,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:42:40.000Z","msg":"為左部電話跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6ffae4302fb6ed6a913759af74031c9fa346b5","tid":193762,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"肯定唔係咁簡單<br />\n平時已經發生好多唔開心野"},{"pid":"a8a7be26bbbf5f802cf2a9c81b619fd0dc0c37ec","tid":193762,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"小康社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4350af15817d9a67f56a78f18921f571f047f5b","tid":193762,"uid":97576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"飛行模式"},{"pid":"ae08b62ecfe6cb280cee2aba45cb6f72a09f77f7",